{
  "stem": "1901.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 370.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You've seen those pictures of those.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's how it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know how I survived there, no idea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in other words, I nearly went from Auschwitz to Dachau all in-- was about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dachau.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say it was about a week.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, there's documented, seven days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was more than a week, a week, or eight days, or seven days, give me a day-- give and take a day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's quite a distance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the trains didn't go backwards, and forwards, and stop, and then-- and we couldn't get out of it, because the train was locked.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only thing is we could take-- there were little bit windows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we could tug a little bit snow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was all snow in those days, but no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some try to drink their own urine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's-- it was thirst.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no support.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How can you support?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nothing to support anyone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You stay alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and I did stay alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look at him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in Dachau--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I arrived in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I must have had something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Dachau, when we arrived on that railway station, this I remember, even SS collapsed when they saw us coming out of the train.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they opened the wagons, they collapsed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were [NON-ENGLISH] and women standing there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When they saw us, they just fainted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We must have been a sight-- [INAUDIBLE] and nude.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I also remember when we walked from Dachau railway station to camp-- I don't have a distance, the SS walked on the side with a machine gun against the houses that no one must look out of the window.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And warning if they looked, they shoot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we must have been a sight, how we came out of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
